### Iegūst visus kursa rezultātus
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-results
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūst rezultātu pēc ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-results/{{uuid}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūst visus rezultātus pēc kursa ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-results/by-course/{{courseUuid}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Izveido jaunu kursa rezultātu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-results
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": {
    "id": "COURSE_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "category": {
    "id": "CATEGORY_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "language": "lv",
  "learningOutcome": "Studējošais spēj pielietot algoritmus datu analīzē."
}

###

### Atjauno kursa rezultātu
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/course-results/{{uuid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": {
    "id": "COURSE_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "category": {
    "id": "CATEGORY_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "language": "lv",
  "learningOutcome": "Atjaunināts rezultāts ar uzlabotu formulējumu."
}

###

### Dzēš kursa rezultātu
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/course-results/{{uuid}}
